-- MOVES-Keith Scott joins Brooks Macdonald from Blackfinch Investments
-- 
-- Mon Sep 22, 2014 06:17AM EDT
-- None



Sept 22 (Reuters) - Investment manager Brooks Macdonald Asset Management Ltd said it appointed Keith Scott as business development manager.

Scott, who joins from Blackfinch Investments, will be based in Brooks Macdonald's Leamington Spa office in the UK. He will be responsible for developing professional adviser and intermediary relationships in the Midlands region, Brooks Macdonald said in a statement.